  APRIL 21 at&nbsp\;&nbsp\;METRO&nbsp\;VENDÔME\nMÉTRO VENDOME 5160 boul. 
 de Maisonneuve West\, Montreal\, Quebec\, Canada\nJOIN US AT THE PAJU VIGI
 LS Vigil and distribution PAJU Palestine: &nbsp\; TUESDAY APRIL 21 at&nbsp
 \;&nbsp\;METRO&nbsp\;VENDÔME TUESDAY&nbsp\;APRIL 21&nbsp\;&nbsp\;FROM 4 P
